WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.195
Management is largely supportive.

00:00:02.195 --> 00:00:05.488
Guideline-directed heart failure therapy anchors treatment.

00:00:05.488 --> 00:00:08.781
Fulminant presentations require early mechanical circulatory

00:00:08.781 --> 00:00:09.330
support.

00:00:09.330 --> 00:00:12.623
Immunosuppression is reserved for giant cell,

00:00:12.623 --> 00:00:14.819
sarcoid, and immune-checkpoint myocarditis.

00:00:14.819 --> 00:00:18.112
Most patients recover fully; exercise restriction

00:00:18.112 --> 00:00:21.405
for three to six months reduces

00:00:21.405 --> 00:00:23.600
arrhythmic risk during recovery.
